title: Introducing: We Talk Back Podcast
itunes:title: Introducing: We Talk Back Podcast
description:
Hosted by two unapologetically black women with an opinion who talk back, TamBam and AJ! Helping women maneuver through the Sea of Men, We Talk Back” podcast is here to guide femineity to it’s ultimate greatness. We talk Back podcast is giving their listeners the raw and unfiltered comedic gift of repartee. With thought-provoking conversations about sex, relationships, and money with a dash of danger and glitter. TamBam & AJ will also help listeners seeking non-professional guidance, as these ladies deliver advice and their personal thoughts on topics.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
